Description: Small thick, copper coin, crudely made and roughly circular. An incised roughly circular line, runs around both faces 1mm from the edge. Any writing or design on the faces is not visible.
Findspot: Excavated/Findspot: Kulubnarti, 21-S-2 House E5 Fill south-west of House E2
